title: AC/DC - The Bon Scott Years
description:
This is everything Bon recorded with AC/DC that has been officially released.
The six studio albums are in their original Australian configurations.
The first four (High Voltage, TNT, Dirty Deeds and Let There Be Rock) have been remastered, based on the 94/95 masters, but with full-length versions instead of US-edits and the Australian-only tracks have been volume matched.
Live In Paris is now one seamless show.
Live Wires collects all other Bon-related tracks officially released, mostly from Volts and Backtracks.

FLAC files with ReplayGain.

* High Voltage
* TNT
* Dirty Deeds Done Dirt Cheap
* Let There Be Rock
* Live from the Atlantic Studios
* Powerage
* If You Want Blood (You Got It)
* Highway to Hell
* Let There Be Rock - The Movie - Live in Paris
* Live Wires
